OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773052871
OL,3,CGirl, 15, dies after collapsing during
OL,4,Cfootball match
OL,6,FA 15-year-old girl has died after
OL,7,Fcollapsing during a football match, a
OL,8,Fclub has announed.
OL,10,FOxford United Academy player, Amelia
OL,11,FAplin had been playing in a match
OL,12,Fagainst Fulham on Saturday afternoon
OL,13,F(7 March) at the club's training
OL,14,Fcentre, when a "serious medical
OL,15,Fincident" took place.
OL,17,FOxford United released a statement
OL,18,Ftoday (Sunday 8 March) saying: "It is
OL,19,Fwith immense sadness that we announce
OL,20,Fthe passing of 15-year-old Academy
OL,21,Fplayer, Amelia Aplin."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
