PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773052871
OL,3,CGirl, 15, dies after collapsing during
OL,4,Cfootball match
OL,6,FIt added, the club's "thoughts and
OL,7,Fcondolences are with Amelia's family,
OL,8,Ffriend, teammates and coaches".
OL,10,FSunday's game between Oxford United
OL,11,FWomen and Real Bedford has been
OL,12,Fpostponed.
OL,14,FThe statement continued: "Amelia
OL,15,Fcollapsed during a Girls' Academy game
OL,16,Fagainst Fulham at the Club's Training
OL,17,FCentre in Horspath yesterday afternoon.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
