PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1773052871
OL,3,CGirl, 15, dies after collapsing during
OL,4,Cfootball match
OL,6,F"The thoughts and sincere condolences
OL,7,Ffrom everyone at Oxford United are
OL,8,Fwith Amelia's family, friends,
OL,9,Fteammates and coaches.
OL,11,F"We would like to place on record our
OL,12,Fappreciation for the efforts of the
OL,13,Fmedical staff at both Oxford United
OL,14,Fand Fulham Football Club, along with
OL,15,Fthe emergency services.
OL,17,F"The Club will offer support to
OL,18,FAmelia's family, players, coaches and
OL,19,Fstaff impacted by this tragic event.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
